We're planning on doing a benefit concert for Ukrainian refugees in Romania this Thursday at 7p doors / 7:30p show CT. The event is to be held in our nearly-finished(!!) studio in Nashville. We're planning on playing in-the-round with Ellie Turner, Tyler Moody and Taylor Kelly. If you're in the Nashville area and would like to come, please shoot us a text at 615-829-6895 and if we've got room, we plan on letting you know.

The event is scheduled to stream for free online via Facebook Live and Instagram Live. We ask that you'd be generous in donating.
